  "texts": [
    "Although NVMain 2.0 allows to estimate energy consumption metrics based on the results of circuit-level simulations, it has limitations.",
    "Since it focuses on memory-oriented simulations of emerging non-volatile structures it does not support the inclusion of the peripheral circuitry that would be necessary to model compute-inmemory architectures.",
    "To overcome this challenge, Xia et al.",
    "240 presented MNSIM and Zhu et al. presented the successor MNSIM 2.0 241.",
    "The simulator uses a behavioural model to estimate the worst case and average accuracy which significantly improves the performance of the simulation."
